{"tid":1812281,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家好好珍邊嘅每一位","createTime":"2020-01-05T11:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T14:51:09.000Z","uid":193780,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f997dc2ad8450e750428410a927963c7fde455c0","tid":1812281,"uid":193780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"依場運動嚟到2020年1月5號 經歷左210日<br />\n<br />\n被補人士有6960人<br />\n我地失去左好多手足、家人、時間、甚至愛你嘅人 <br />\n<br />\n依場活動時至今日 已經唔可以再係以前咁 <br />\n隨時隨地開花、陣地、快閃、行街<br />\n不論你係街坊、和理非、勇武都會有被補嘅一刻<br />\n<br />\n2020年係要轉型嘅一年 將會係全面罷工<br />\n<br />\n和理非：盡力叫身邊每一個有工作嘅人 入工會 好重要 你唔講佢地真唔知 不停做文宣 比更多人知道香港嘅問題 <br />\n<br />\n學生：你地要好好保護你地嘅老師 因為佢地為左你地可以連工都冇 同埋要記得每一個數字 <br />\n<br />\n勇武：依段時間你地好好休息 裝備自己 多啲同你屋企人、朋友、愛人相處 <br />\n<br />\n當大家知道身邊嘅人被補 唔好一句說話都唔講 <br />\n因為你地每一句說話都係推動我地繼續行前落去 <br />\n無論你識唔識佢好 都希望你地可以踏前一步 <br />\n作出關心同安慰佢地<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好學我 當你失去左先嚟後悔 就已經太遲 <br />\n好好珍惜身邊每一個人 為你所做嘅嘢 <br />\n無論你發生咩事 我都會為你挺身而出<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n兄弟爬山 齊上齊落<br />\n一個都不能少<br />\n你唔認輸就冇人打得死你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y8Eu0bx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8Eu0bx.jpg&h=c3ff2129&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QejiTwy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQejiTwy.jpg&h=82b8d93f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pM5ywy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pM5ywy.jpg&h=30baa81d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63a23f930838d67a9dfb5891fcb9ca9e29766343","tid":1812281,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"各位手足，同意與否，請聽我一言，睇哂佢，Spread出去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1812233/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1812233/page/1#preview</a><br />\n<br />\n我P牌推唔到 唯有咁樣推比大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ed8821f0e2d1b2bcbb2fc8549faf9b7eb8ab86","tid":1812281,"uid":241453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad53158e0ce5fbc7d458faa2a4a60ff91ef18455","tid":1812281,"uid":72991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b747d892dcceaeee71d9d410fc8880ab23ff09","tid":1812281,"uid":79278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}